TwitterBird
===========

Creates a model to cache Tweets since twitter fails all the time.
Provides a helper that outputs the typical tweet area and takes care of caching.
Installs a twitter_bird CSS file as well.

Install
=======

Simply install the plugin
script/generate twitter_bird_migration
rake db:migrate
Edit config/twitter_bird.yml

Then use
=twitter_bird

in your views.

Modify the CSS file to your liking.

